# Agricultural Chatbot - Environment Variables

## Backend (.env)
PORT=5001
MONGO_URI=mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/agri_chatbot
ML_API_URL=http://localhost:6000

## ML API (.env in ml-model/)
FLASK_PORT=6000
DATASET_PATH=../dataset/final_modified_dataset.xlsx

## Frontend (.env.local in frontend/)
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5001

---

### Production Deployment
For production, replace:
- localhost with actual domain/IP
- mongodb://127.0.0.1 with MongoDB Atlas connection string
- Add CORS origin configuration

### MongoDB Atlas Setup (Optional)
1. Create cluster at https://www.mongodb.com/cloud/atlas
2. Get connection string: mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/agri_chatbot
3. Update MONGO_URI in backend/.env
4. Ensure "agri_chatbot" database exists in Atlas
